{"tid":1311492,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[新手買車]每月油費預計問題","createTime":"2019-07-13T08:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T12:22:50.000Z","uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0c0b2464fe8da25a9cd6df74d3e95041c0ca6f3a","tid":1311492,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得對新手黎講, 油費真係好難預。<br />\n我打算就出部fit/jazz, 上網睇D 人share, 油耗就大概15-20公里/L,<br />\n我宜家計數, 就當10公里/L好了。<br />\n上google map睇屋企同公司就23公里,我就當30公里好了。<br />\n姐係每日來回行60公里, 每日用6升油。<br />\n宜家油費每升唔過$20, 我又當$20/L好了 (我都係上網睇)<br />\n咁每日就係6升*$20 = $120。<br />\n當我每月番22日工計 = 22*$120 = $2640<br />\n<br />\n或者第二個計法, fit/jazz 油箱 40L, <br />\n打爆 40*$20 = $800 <br />\n每個星期都打爆一次, 800*4 = 一個月$3200。<br />\n<br />\n再預鬆D...假期出街....預每月$3500...<br />\n合理嗎?<br />\n咁計岩嗎?"},{"pid":"be2b64b0a6ed52ec3abed2476d344f1f13365a22","tid":1311492,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"你條數會唔會計得太過痴線<br />\nJazz 行60km 頂晒壟 $70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319ad64fbb1988602acf838108c9c858982cdc53","tid":1311492,"uid":73,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T08:26:17.000Z","msg":"使唔使預得咁撚鬆呀..."},{"pid":"8ab95f92b5ee8dedf437d5f72920722cbd9a38c7","tid":1311492,"uid":130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"be2b64b0a6ed52ec3abed2476d344f1f13365a22","tid":1311492,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"你條數會唔會計得太過痴線<br />\nJazz 行60km 頂晒壟 $70<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T08:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知啊。<br />\n剩係諗住預鬆好過預緊🤦&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"b1d14cd8f1f2f8d211bb7457c5dad5809e604240","tid":1311492,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab95f92b5ee8dedf437d